"{\"uid\": \"newstalk.com-news-hosting-2072-olympics-would-celebrate-150-years-of-irish-independence-senator-1754370\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Live 19:00-22:00 19.38 12 Aug 2024 Share this article 19.38 12 Aug 2024 Share this article Hosting the Olympic Games in 2072 would be a fitting way to celebrate 150 of Ireland's participation as an independent nation, a Fianna F\\u00e1il Senator has said.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 174, \"end\": 181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999879400422365, \"rank\": 1.1085127232586342e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 226, \"end\": 237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fianna_F\\u00e1il\", \"score\": 0.9999999994315658, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fianna F\\u00e1il\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fianna_F\\u00e1il\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fianna_F\\u00e1il\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this article\", \"from\": 41, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \"this article\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 90}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 99, \"to\": 116}, {\"ngram\": \"a fitting way\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 147}, {\"ngram\": \"an independent nation\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ireland has never hosted the Olympics and currently lacks the sporting and public transport infrastructure for a successful bid.\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 257, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999879400422365, \"rank\": 1.1085127232586342e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 294}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting and public transport infrastructure\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 363}, {\"ngram\": \"a successful bid\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Senator Malcolm Byrne said Ireland needs to be \\\"ambitious\\\" as a country and should start laying the groundwork for a bid now.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 404, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malcolm_Byrne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Malcolm Byrne\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malcolm_Byrne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malcolm_Byrne\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999879400422365, \"rank\": 1.1085127232586342e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a country\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"the groundwork\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"a bid\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Why I like the idea of 2072 is that it marks 150 years since Ireland as an independent State first started taking part in the Olympics,\\\" he toldLunchtime Live.\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 587, \"end\": 594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999879400422365, \"rank\": 1.1085127232586342e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"150 years\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"an independent State\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I appreciate it's five decades away but I think one of our challenges in this country is that we have not engaged a lot in long-term planning and I think we need to look at engaging in a lot more long-term planning.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our challenges\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"this country\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"long-term planning\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot more long-term planning\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We also need to talk about the type of infrastructure that we need to be able to support our elite athletes.\\\"\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the type\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"infrastructure\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"our elite athletes\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The atmosphere is electric at the#Olympicteam homecoming ?pic.twitter.com/LqWbCAHG4C - NewstalkFM (@NewstalkFM)August 12, 2024 Senator Byrne said he could understand why many people who think an Irish bid for the Olympics would seem unlikely to succeed at the moment.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1156, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_John_Byrne\", \"score\": 0.8229190579868942, \"rank\": 0.215186341922043, \"text\": \"Byrne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_John_Byrne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_John_Byrne\"}, {\"begin\": 1216, \"end\": 1221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.947168903278524, \"rank\": 0.0376977258910